Politely point out that you wont pay hard cash for a game that is degenerating into frustration and anger because of the actions of a select few.<br>
Tell them enforce the rules or people will move to DAoC.<br>
Corporations always respond well to the threat of reduction of their bottom line profits <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
